7.2. Effect of Termination of License.

Upon termination of this Public License, all legal rights that were necessary for Licensor, subject to the termination of this Public License, to enforce this Public License shall survive such termination.

8.1. For the avoidance of doubt, the Licensor offers to the public the right to use the Work under the terms of this Public License (his/her “Initial Offer”). The Licensor reserves the right to terminate his/her offer on the event of:

